ddf.catalog.data.impl

Class MetacardTypeImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • ddf.catalog.data.impl.MetacardTypeImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MetacardType, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CswRecordMetacardType, FeatureMetacardType, GmdMetacardType, QualifiedMetacardTypeImpl, RegistryObjectMetacardType

    public class MetacardTypeImpl
extends Object
implements MetacardType
    Default implementation of the MetacardType, used by BasicTypes to create the BasicTypes.BASIC_METACARD.

    This class is Serializable and care should be taken with compatibility if changes are made.

    For what constitutes a compatible change in serialization, see Sun's Guidelines.

    Author:
    ddf.isgs@lmco.com
